## Write a program to print elements of an array

```txt
Input  : [1, 2, 3, 4, 5]
Output : 1 2 3 4 5
```

---

<CodeBlock slug="print-elements-of-an-array" >

```c
# include <stdio.h>

// Prints int array
void PrintArray(int *array)
{
	int len = sizeof(array);
	for (int i = 0; i < len; ++i)
	{
		printf("%d\n", array[i]);
	}
}

void main()
{
	int array[] = {1, 2, 3, 4};
	PrintArray(array);
}
```

